<para>Invoked on the reader thread once per turn, immediately after <computeroutput>TurnComplete</computeroutput> arrives. Covers both client-initiated turns (via <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_agent_proxy_1acac838d4e56195490697f75f87bf2030" kindref="member">SendText</ref>) and server-initiated turns (voice autosend).</para>
