        <briefdescription>
<para>Send a text message to the agent (fire-and-forget). </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Enqueues the message and returns immediately. The response arrives through the persistent callbacks registered via <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_agent_proxy_1ab7977336473dd8678e26ca747b9cbaf4" kindref="member">SetOnAnswerText</ref>, <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_agent_proxy_1a9ee0574c5ab152a47de8beb2cb4aee10" kindref="member">SetOnTurnComplete</ref>, and <ref refid="class_tryll_1_1_agent_proxy_1a83c6893938918c7d7c8fcc559d7d75aa" kindref="member">SetOnError</ref>. Register those callbacks before the first <computeroutput>SendText</computeroutput> call.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>text</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>User-turn text to send. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
